{"tid":1495262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2017年勇武派突襲「港漂家」大圍地舖沒有被捕","createTime":"2019-08-22T03:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T23:00:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62048e41252f7fd90cde4f79dd9fb0ba2afbdcff","tid":1495262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/93620/天眼直擊-為內地人搵屋港漂家-遭口罩男刑毀-創辦人-唔理性\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F93620%2F%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%BC%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%90%B5%E5%B1%8B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%82%E5%AE%B6-%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80-%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA-%E5%94%94%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=c6fdf236\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/93620/天眼直擊-為內地人搵屋港漂家-遭口罩男刑毀-創辦人-唔理性</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/601576/org/eed3c37a8fe56c47d5f1fb73bc51011c.jpg/ZasVP5LXJYFUfYZwnY7xOMfHO9O5_6ciKaIrbimiK24?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F601576%2Forg%2Feed3c37a8fe56c47d5f1fb73bc51011c.jpg%2FZasVP5LXJYFUfYZwnY7xOMfHO9O5_6ciKaIrbimiK24%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1d883c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左：案發後的「港漂家」大圍地舖（黃偉民攝）／右：案發後的「港漂家」觀塘工廈辦公室（魯嘉裕攝）<br />\n<br />\n五分鐘內兩辦事處被襲<br />\n<br />\n今日下午近兩時，大圍及觀塘於5分鐘內，分別發生兩宗刑事毀壞案，受害者是同一公司。「港漂家」於兩區的辦事處，分別被兩名戴口罩的男子持硬物打爆玻璃門，玻璃碎滿一地，一名女顧客頭部受傷送院，事件中暫未有人被捕，警方正追緝涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘辦公室首先被毀<br />\n<br />\n第一宗案件在下午1時37分發生，「港漂家」位於觀塘開源道的工廈辦公室，一名男職員報案，指兩名男子打破公司玻璃門後逃去，辦公室內的3部電腦、影印機及膠盒亦有損毀。五分鐘後，一名職員報案指，位於大圍積運街2號海福花園的「港漂家」地舖，有人打玻其玻璃門。警方到場後發現，其電爐、電視及窗部均有損毀，在場一名45歲女子頭部受傷，被送院治理。口罩男犯案手法熟練，在15秒內完成整個過程並離去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/601582/org/33aed00f15374c5172bfffe12679d45e.jpg/H_SkdRPBqly3hezOZ-ez8U9359H_nxKqcnqlTXJ6pU0?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F601582%2Forg%2F33aed00f15374c5172bfffe12679d45e.jpg%2FH_SkdRPBqly3hezOZ-ez8U9359H_nxKqcnqlTXJ6pU0%3Fv%3Dw960&h=0f0d9a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「港漂家」觀塘工廈辦公室內一片混亂。（魯嘉裕攝）<br />\n<br />\n未及阻止口罩男已逃去 一女客受傷<br />\n<br />\n記者事後取得大圍地舖事發時的閉路電視片段顯示，一名黑衣人首先推開玻璃門，順手搶去近門口桌上一部手提電腦後，向旁邊一人擲去，然後再摧毀一部電視機。另一黑衣人緊隨其後，疑似有動作，向玻璃門近地面處攻擊。整個過程不足10秒，店內近10名人士未及阻止，兩人已經逃去。根據負責人提供的相片，可見已碎裂的玻璃門出現一個圓形缺口，疑似被硬物損毀。負責人Ken表示，傷者為一名女顧客，事發時正在與女兒簽約，幸治理後已無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/601580/org/9c895880711eba2460e2d30a3be7a8c2.png/oKtX4Q6BLKasvRpLZdY5jXT7_iw4E5pbonV10qJ1ddI?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F601580%2Forg%2F9c895880711eba2460e2d30a3be7a8c2.png%2FoKtX4Q6BLKasvRpLZdY5jXT7_iw4E5pbonV10qJ1ddI%3Fv%3Dw960&h=23e0e793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n閉路電視片段拍得兩名黑衣人戴口罩到「港漂家」大圍地鋪搗亂。（片段截圖）<br />\n<br />\n或不再貼簡體字<br />\n<br />\n劉直指其公司「冇政治立場，純粹做生意&hellip;&hellip;至於呢啲政治嘅野，唔想理&hellip;&hellip;」但事件發生後恐怕「逼我地要理」，或會考慮一下改變營銷策略，例如店舖不用簡體字招牌。劉坦言，覺得犯案者「好唔理性，好恐怖，將香港搗亂」，強調表達意見有很多方法，不需使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/601586/org/bd84573ec07bbb18696ca6d52c51094f.jpg/hiew7cTbEbkSMyS-RZoFP1lf2Goc8JLu5XO-4OVzvuA?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F601586%2Forg%2Fbd84573ec07bbb18696ca6d52c51094f.jpg%2Fhiew7cTbEbkSMyS-RZoFP1lf2Goc8JLu5XO-4OVzvuA%3Fv%3Dw960&h=bab07908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「港漂家」負責人劉瑞卿（黃偉民攝）"},{"pid":"d33ddf8b9f7654b43af41f606b098aa8a58808e0","tid":1495262,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"支那"},{"pid":"1a8528600c5de7194c6a3b7905b2ceab8a3fd172","tid":1495262,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2EWgtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2EWgtZ.jpg&h=a914effb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無大台既民主運動應該有無大台既籌款平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495157</a>"},{"pid":"45bc5b633e6e91fc6de08c5df410c7ad7f4976de","tid":1495262,"uid":122386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔比係生意糾紛? 欠人錢? 同行出手?<br />\n<br />\n唔好一黎就話係勇武做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbee9cfbb1faaf35df76708e532aed6c1184a646","tid":1495262,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45bc5b633e6e91fc6de08c5df410c7ad7f4976de","tid":1495262,"uid":122386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔比係生意糾紛? 欠人錢? 同行出手?<br />\n<br />\n唔好一黎就話係勇武做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"明顯藍絲黎啦 扑得"},{"pid":"3a5167e0240cb5b28e80b7b240abeb1b470b97f6","tid":1495262,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45bc5b633e6e91fc6de08c5df410c7ad7f4976de","tid":1495262,"uid":122386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔比係生意糾紛? 欠人錢? 同行出手?<br />\n<br />\n唔好一黎就話係勇武做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"2017年架單野 關依家咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又搶野又連爆兩間分店好明顯係尋仇"},{"pid":"3585c515c9f5644d132c5cf580715ccb7a2b7d7f","tid":1495262,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">觀塘鴻圖道71號瀝洋工業大廈9樓<br />\n營業中</span></span>"},{"pid":"5083b25fcf50cc55a85c14bb4596ae00f